<div>
  <div class="profile-background-div">
{{#if user}}
  <h1>Welcome {{user.username}}!</h1>   
   
{{#if profiles}}
<p>Click on any of your profiles below and check out the latest news, league standings, and more related to your favorite team.
<h3>Your profiles:</h3>
  <div class='my-profile'>
  {{#each profiles}}
  <div class="full-card">

    <div class="profile-box">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/profile/{{this._id}}"><img src="{{this.picture}}" alt="avatar picture" class="avatar-picture"></a></li>
        <li  class="card-name">
          <br>
        <a href="/profile/{{this._id}}"><h4>{{this.name}}</h4></a>
        </li>
        {{!-- <li>Favorite team: {{this.favoriteTeam}} --}}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-box-buttons-div">
      <button class="bttn-sign-in"><a href="/private/edit/{{this._id}}" class="edit-button">Edit profile</a></button>
        <form action="/private/delete/{{this._id}}" method="POST">
          <button>Delete Profile</button>
        </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/each}}
  </div>
{{else}}
  <p>Thanks for joining the Live Football Updates family! We've noticed you haven't created any profiles yet. To start enjoying this app, the first step is to <a href='/private/create-profile'>Create a profile</a>, selecting your favorite team from La Liga, the Serie A, or the Premier League.</p>
  <p>Once your profile is created, click on it and check out the latest news, league standings, and more related to your favorite team.
  <form action="/private/create-profile">
    <input type="submit" value="Create profile" />
  </form>
{{/if}}
{{/if}}



  </div>
</div>